==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Fillister
<hw>Fil"lis*ter</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The
rabbet on the outer edge of a sash bar to hold the glass and the
putty.</def> <rj><au>Knight.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A plane for making a rabbet.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Fillister screw had</b></col>, <cd>a short cylindrical
screw head, having a convex top.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Filly</ent>⟦br⟧
